The '''Holorepository''' was a library on the [[wheelworld]] ''[[Arkam 13]]'' where [[Atour Riten]] once worked as an archivist. It was believed by many to have one of the largest collections of lore on the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Old Republic]], greater than even the [[Jedi Archives/Legends|Jedi Archives]] in the [[Jedi Temple/Legends|Jedi Temple]].

